---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About — ScriptFlow"
	description="ScriptFlow is a free, private, browser-based transcription tool. Learn how it works and why it's free."
	canonicalPath="/about"
>
	<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[#2B2013]">About ScriptFlow</h1>
	<div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-[#5C4F3D]">
		<p>
			ScriptFlow is a single, focused tool: turning audio and video into
			text. It runs entirely in your web browser using WebAssembly and an
			on-device machine learning model — no file you upload is ever sent
			to a server.
		</p>
		<p>
			Because there is no server-side processing, ScriptFlow can stay
			completely free with no account, no watermark, and no file-size
			games. The site is supported by on-page advertising.
		</p>
		<p>
			Longer files can take longer to transcribe on older devices since
			the work happens on your own hardware rather than in the cloud.
		</p>
	</div>
</Layout>
